{"tid":2417233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公民記者採訪白羅斯抗爭｜ 見證香港輸出革命","createTime":"2021-02-21T16:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T02:29:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4635077a1a3f388bfc075e9b226013817eecec1e","tid":2417233,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"公民記者採訪白羅斯抗爭｜<br />\n見證香港輸出革命 <br />\n#壹仔專題​－壹週刊 Next <br />\n原刊日期：20210210<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/10UN_402UXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F10UN_402UXw&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=9fcfdb25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/10UN_402UXw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壹週刊 NEXT<br />\n718K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n香港原本沒有「戰地記者」這物種，經過2019年的槍林彈雨後，培養出大量。到了2020年，世界各地抗爭運動燎原，泰國、緬甸、白羅斯，不願做奴隸的人們紛紛站起來。年僅25歲的陳子煜（Alex）是公民記者，以相機記錄反修例運動，作品見於本地和日本的網媒。隨著香港的抗爭沉靜下來，他開始放眼世界：「香港人叫國際社會關注香港，會唔會香港人都要關注國際，睇吓其他地方發生什麼事？」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/ICPUAaLOKdb​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2FICPUAaLOKdb%E2%80%8B&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=cbd57c8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/ICPUAaLOKdb​</a><br />\n-----------------------------"},{"pid":"8e0e648e758ba9ec03f1a2f77947b8d32aed3d02","tid":2417233,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f187a9f372d47ee32b04f8c7d7f14fc44ae41a3b","tid":2417233,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a676743ded4d27b1366eb013d7e155d26f8caf","tid":2417233,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"但香港係輸撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},